 he is only concerned with the rights of gay people .


root(ROOT-0, concerned-4)
nsubjpass(concerned-4, he-1)
auxpass(concerned-4, is-2)
advmod(concerned-4, only-3)
det(rights-7, the-6)
prep_with(concerned-4, rights-7)
amod(people-10, gay-9)
prep_of(rights-7, people-10)

  He  suggests that this opinion on the topic of homosexuality is unique to America , claiming that Evangelical Christians in Spain are not actively opposed to civil unions despite sharing the same religious belief systems .  
root(ROOT-0, suggests-2)
